  "detailed_description": "HELLFRONT is an intense multiplayer Top-Down shooter with a tactical twist. Conquer ground, build a base, produce fighters and give them your orders. <br><br>Play the campaign Solo or Co-Op - or crush your friends in insanely intense PVP combat with up to four players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824460/extras/99ae5e3725a59bd88fb54fed7f5046ec.poster.avif?t=1716457801\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824460/extras/99ae5e3725a59bd88fb54fed7f5046ec.webm?t=1716457801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/824460/extras/99ae5e3725a59bd88fb54fed7f5046ec.mp4?t=1716457801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A multiplayer Top-Down shooter with a unique tactical twist.<br></li><li> Glorious, intense PVP combat with up to four players, online or local.<br></li><li> Three Co-Op campaigns played alone or with a friend, online or local.<br></li><li> Rapid, intense matches. It never drags!<br></li><li> Speedrun and compete on the leaderboards!<br></li><li> Play with mouse & keyboard or gamepad.</li></ul>",
